  "text": "The research approach we used in our survey is the Goal, Question, Metric (GQM) [CITATION_1] . Stated using it template, the goal of our survey was to understand the state-of-the-practice of modeling in the embedded software domain by identifying to what degree, why and how modeling is conducted.",
